      "title": "5 lakh fine for 4 eggs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Palangoda Deputy Magistrate A. imposed a fine of five lakh rupees on a trader for selling eggs at a higher price than the fixed price at a trading post in Palangoda. Amy. S. Mrs. Menike ordered.",
        "Consumer authority officials said that Rs 65 per egg is Rs 260 for four eggs. (R)"
      ],
